"msg":"湯渣咁撚柒係都要凸個龜頭廢噏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92776df4307798226795971401db2e06882a452b","tid":686633,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T13:34:59.000Z","msg":"Sokam Tam 人性就是這樣，一旦涉及自身或行業利益，就會打横行，無視法律。香港人違法之後，最常說的一句話：我唔知噃！我唔識字噃！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sokam.tam.16?fref=ufi&amp;rc=p\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsokam.tam.16%3Ffref%3Dufi%26rc%3Dp&d=KZr3dx1hxODI1fEvkQuDHQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=14f126d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sokam.tam.16?fref=ufi&amp;rc=p</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n11哥大把亞婆照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760ee1366be327a4127f73a63892b8874c6e50c3","tid":686633,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T01:04:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">淚</span></strong></span></blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">灑</span></span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">雪</span></strong></span>"}]}